
STEP:01
==========
Add/modify the parameters in your <devsuite_home>/forms/server/formsweb.cfg file:
# Forms applet parameter
width=100%
# Forms applet parameter
height=100%



STEP:02
===========
On WHEN_NEW_FROM_INSTANCE trigger

SET_WINDOW_PROPERTY('WINDOW1',window_state, maximize);
SET_WINDOW_PROPERTY(forms_mdi_window,window_state, maximize);
